HOUSE BILL 2587
By Vaughan
SENATE BILL 2322
By Haile
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 5;
Title 6; Title 7; Title 13 and Title 67, relative to
property development.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 13-7-203(a), is amended by deleting
the language "twenty-one (21) calendar days" and substituting "fourteen (14) calendar days".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
